text: Ypsolopha nigrofasciata is a moth of the family Ypsolophidae. It is known from China (Hebei) and the Russian Far East.New taxonomic data on the genus Ypsolopha Latreille (Lepidoptera, Ypsolophidae) with descriptions of two new species from the Russian Far East ==References== Category:Moths described in 1977 Category:Ypsolophidae Category:Moths of Asia
title: Ypsolopha nigrofasciata
